  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "About this dashboard",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 3,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Frontend RUM (Real User Monitoring) for the Angular SPA via Grafana Faro.** The `faro` receiver + traces/logs pipeline are **live** in the otel-collector (browser \u2192 collector \u2192 Grafana Cloud). Panels populate **once the Angular app is instrumented with the Faro Web SDK** \u2014 see the *Frontend observability roadmap* in `docs/202`. Data model: Faro beacon \u2192 OTLP \u2192 Loki (labels `service_name`=Faro app, `deployment_environment`, `kind`\u2208{log,measurement,exception,event}) + Tempo (browser spans). Web-Vitals thresholds follow Google's good/needs-improvement/poor bands."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Overview",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 3
      },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Sessions",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "grafanacloud-logs"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 4,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "grafanacloud-logs"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "count(count by (session_id)(count_over_time({service_name=\"$app\", deployment_environment=\"$deployment_environment\"} | logfmt | session_id!=\"\" [$__range])))",
          "queryType": "instant",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              }
            ]
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
